  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Access</strong> Member of a secret society</p>\n<hr />\n<p>These innocuous, colorless drops can be poured directly into a victim's mouth, or slipped into their food or drink. They initially haze a victim's mind slightly, making them easier to fool; in later stages, they can lead to the victim entering a murderous @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} state. Secret societies use these drops to befuddle a target or to frame them for violence.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:18];</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong> 5 minutes;</p>\n<p><strong>Maximum Duration</strong> 1 hour;</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 1</strong> @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.e1XGnhKNSQIm5IXg]{Stupefied 1} (10 minutes);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 2</strong> stupefied 1 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.i3OJZU2nk64Df3xm]{Clumsy 1} (20 minutes);</p>\n<p><strong>Stage 3</strong> stupefied 1, clumsy 1, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} (30 minutes)</p>"
